# Implementation Plan - Feature Enhancements for Avani Loan Agents

This plan outlines the design and implementation to address the following requests for the **Avani Loan Agents** application:
1. **Employment History**: Add a feature to collect loan applicants' employment history.
2. **SQLite Database Sync Fix**: Diagnose and fix why new customer inquiries are not being saved to the database.
3. **Responsive Loan Calculator**: Create/improve a premium, fully responsive interactive loan calculator widget on the homepage.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Key Database & UI Modifications**
> 1. **Schema Update**: We will add an `employment_history` column to the `leads` table. If SQLite mode is active, the database table will automatically update its schema.
> 2. **Home Page Calculator Integration**: We will build a brand new premium React-based loan calculator directly on the homepage, allowing clients to slide values and click to consult the AI Advisor.
> 3. **Chat URL Query Integration**: The calculator on the homepage will redirect to the AI Advisor chat, pre-seeding the loan details in the chatbot prompt so the client doesn't need to re-enter them.

