## Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Database & AI Route Enhancements (Backend)

#### [MODIFY] [client.ts](file:///c:/Users/ALPHA-1/Desktop/AVANI%20LOAN%20AGENTS/lib/db/client.ts)
- Add `employment_history?: string` to the `Lead` TypeScript interface.
- Add `employment_history TEXT` to the SQLite `CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS leads` statement.
- Update `saveLead` to include `employment_history` in both the column names and parameters list.
- **Bug Fix**: In JSON fallback mode, change `db.run('', [...])` to `db.run('INSERT INTO leads', [...])`. Currently, the mock DB client's `run` method filters on `sql.includes('INSERT INTO leads')`. Because the fallback code passed an empty string `''` as SQL, it skipped database insertion entirely, causing leads to not be saved.

