## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- We will execute the dev build and verification to ensure there are no TypeScript or Next.js build errors.
- We will run the seeder script or check database contents to confirm the `employment_history` column is added and populated.

### Manual Verification
- Navigate to `http://localhost:3000/` and interact with the new Loan Calculator sliders. Check responsiveness across mobile/desktop screen sizes.
- Click *"Apply & Pre-Qualify with AI"* and verify it transfers the state to the chat interface.
- Complete an AI eligibility check chat, approve database submission, and verify the lead is successfully stored.
- Check the Leads Dashboard at `http://localhost:3000/dashboard` to verify the lead details and employment history are correctly saved and loaded from the SQLite database.
